data.description: Attention all investors! If you're looking for a great location inside Stroudsburg this house is for you. This house needs some TLC but it can be a wonderful gem for a person just starting out in life or a person/couple looking to downsize! It has a nice yard for entertaining and overlooks lower Stroudsburg. It has a one-car garage with a wide driveway! The owner is motivated to SELL so bring your reasonable offers today.
